{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_09_01_short",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 想いに応えたい (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After a while‚ Moon Tempest became one of the BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n今日の収録は長丁場でしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your hard work‚ {user}-san\nWe had long recording schedules today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 8.7666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。しかし三本録りの予定が\n急遽一本増えるとは思わなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job. We were only scheduled to record three songs‚ but\nI didn't expect an extra one to be added suddenly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "疲れているところ悪いんだが、帰る前に\n明日の予定をもう一度確認しておこうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to bother you when you're tired‚ but before we go home‚\nlet's check tomorrow's schedule one more time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.033332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 21.0666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "午前中にライブの打ち合わせ、午後にラジオ収録と\nインタビュー、それから特番のゲスト出演ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A live meeting in the morning‚ radio recording and an interview\nin the afternoon‚ and then a guest appearance on the special program‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今までもそれなりに忙しくさせてもらってると思って\nましたけど……BIG4になった影響は大きいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought we'd been already busy up until now‚ but\nbecoming a BIG4 has had a big impact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.233332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "朝から分刻みのスケジュールだけど、大丈夫か？\nさすがに休む時間が少な過ぎるよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a minute-by-minute schedule from morning‚ are you okay?\nYou really don't have enough time to rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 46.1666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。仕事を受けるかどうかは毎回確認を\nとってくれてるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. You always confirm whether you accept or decline a job\nbefore you take it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6199106369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 53.0666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、サニピがBIG4になった時の目の回るような\n忙しさを目の前で見てましたから。想定内です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I saw firsthand how hectic things were for Sunny Peace\nwhen they became BIG4. It's within expectations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}